      • getKeySerialNumber

        public String getKeySerialNumber()
        Returns the Key Serial Number (KSN) used for the encrypting the data. This field is available only when the encryption type is TRIPLE_DES. TRIPLE_DES is an encryption Algorithm where DES applied 3 times using DUKPT.
        Returns:
        Returns key serial number.
